# Niernen Quicksilver
>The iron queen

Niernen was an iron-grey [[Races/Dragon\|dragon]], said to be "like silver," bonded to [[Characters/Michael Witchhunter\|Michael Witchhunter]]. Her body was killed in a fight on the Southern Point by the [[Groups/Fallen Riders\|Fallen Riders]] during the [[Events/Second Rider Rebellion\|Second Rider Rebellion]], after she sacrificed what little life she had left to defend her Rider. 

Because she had released her [[Library/Eldunarí\|Eldunarí]] before her death, she continues to live on inside it. It is a moderately sized, silvery gem that is now being kept by [[Characters/Chevalier\|Chevalier]]. 

Her name means "orchid" in the [[Library/Ancient Language\|Ancient Language]].
